ly quantum linear controller which offers an improvement\nin performance over the classical ones.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Nov 2007 04:30:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 May 2009 09:48:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-07"}
